title: Injured but energetic Fetty Wap performs from seat at show
text:
> Entertainment Injured but energetic Fetty Wap performs from seat at show Singer Nicki Minaj, left, appears as a special guest during rapper Meek Mill's set at Power 105.1's Powerhouse 2015 at Barclays Center on Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015, in New York.
